{"tid":2515463,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony Store嘅職員都未必用Xperia","createTime":"2021-05-04T04:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T04:31:46.000Z","uid":49781,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8eaeb537ea9d28e2b625211aa1e6469d9db43638","tid":2515463,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"前幾日去K11 Sony Store<br />\n見到個Sales職員拎住部S21U同iPhone開工<br />\n其實都幾傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲客見到連職員都唔用Xperia嘅時候<br />\n咁點sell人買呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係話要強迫員工用Xperia<br />\n人哋打份工啫都有自由揀用咩電話<br />\n但至少你係鋪面都要用公司機呀<br />\n係鋪頭開緊工俾人見到唔用Sony機<br />\n觀感真係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知Samsung Store會唔會咁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旺角Sony Store就醒少少<br />\n起碼會揸住部1仔做嘢<br />\n希望管理層或者路過嘅Sony人見到可以搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便追追1仔5仔個An11更新呀大佬<br />\n全世界淨返香港未有咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多我斯文啲唔屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f83ecc46d509ea415324650297c126824e7b623","tid":2515463,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"開po十秒就有負皮<br />\n懷疑有人follow我見我開po就即刻畀負皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b7d922cb679cc194d5a60e9e57911764a9dc4f","tid":2515463,"uid":305799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"android機我自己覺得p